---
import InvestLayout from '../../layouts/InvestLayout.astro';
import Disclosure from '../../components/Disclosure.astro';
---

<InvestLayout title="Cap Table" titleVi="Bảng cổ phần" noindex={true}>
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16" aria-label="Bảng cổ phần">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-red-400 border border-red-400/30 rounded-full">Riêng tư</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-gold border border-gold/30 rounded-full">Placeholder</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">Bảng cổ phần</h1>

    <div class="mt-8 bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-bg-border">
            <th class="text-left py-3 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Bên liên quan</th>
            <th class="text-right py-3 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Cổ phần</th>
            <th class="text-right py-3 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Pre-money %</th>
            <th class="text-right py-3 text-ink-muted uppercase text-xs">Post-money %</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-bg-border">
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 text-ink">Nhà sáng lập</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">TBD</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-gold">100%</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-gold">85.71%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 text-ink">Nhà đầu tư seed (mới)</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">TBD</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">0%</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-gold">14.29%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 text-ink">Option pool</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">TBD</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">TBD</td>
            <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink-muted">TBD</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-bg-border">
        <div><span class="text-xs text-ink-dim uppercase">Định giá pre-money</span><div class="text-xl font-bold text-gold">$4.5M</div></div>
        <div><span class="text-xs text-ink-dim uppercase">Số vốn gọi</span><div class="text-xl font-bold text-gold">$750K</div></div>
        <div><span class="text-xs text-ink-dim uppercase">Định giá post-money</span><div class="text-xl font-bold text-gold">$5.25M</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-ink-dim italic">
      Bảng chi tiết với số cổ phần và lịch vesting có khi đầu tư. Không công bố dữ liệu cap table thật.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12"><Disclosure locale="vi" /></div>
  </section>
</InvestLayout>
